---
title: Lamb & Caramelised Onion Cheeseburger  with French Fries, Cucumber Salad & Fancy Truffle Mayo
description: Do you want a game-changing lamb burger? This fancy version will do the trick! There’s the classic additions of gooey Cheddar cheese and saucy caramelised onion, but the real ace in the hole is the truffle mayo layered on the buns - it’s a sure-fire win.
